Sky Deutschland AG (SKYD)  named  James
Murdoch , deputy chief operating officer of majority owner 21st
Century Fox Inc., as chairman of its supervisory board.  Murdoch, who joined the board in April, replaces 21st
Century Fox President and Chief Operating Officer Chase Carey in
the role, according to a statement today. The decision was
reported in June by Manager Magazin.  Carey will remain on Sky Deutschlandâ€™s supervisory board.
Fox owns 53 percent of Sky Deutschland, according to data
